This is not a replacement for medical or psychological care,<break time="1.5s"/> but rather a doorway into your own inner sanctuary,<break time="1.5s"/> where healing has always resided.<break time="3s"/>

Find a comfortable position now.<break time="2s"/>
Perhaps sitting with your spine gently supported,<break time="1.5s"/> or lying down with your body fully relaxed.<break time="2.5s"/>
Ensure you will not be disturbed.<break time="2s"/>
If possible,<break time="700ms"/> wear headphones to receive the full binaural soundscape.<break time="3s"/>

Allow your eyes to close when you feel ready.<break time="2.5s"/>
Take a deep,<break time="700ms"/> nourishing breath.<break time="3s"/>
Breathing in possibility.<break time="2.5s"/>
Breathing out anything you no longer need.<break time="4s"/>

This journey will guide you through layers of consciousness,<break time="1.5s"/> drawing upon the Inner Healer within you,<break time="1.5s"/> the Rose Mother who nurtures all beings,<break time="1.5s"/> and the World Tree Guardian who connects heaven and earth.<break time="3.5s"/>

Simply allow yourself to receive<break time="1.5s"/> whatever insights come naturally.<break time="3s"/>
There is nothing you need to force.<break time="2s"/>
Nothing you need to make happen.<break time="2.5s"/>
Only to listen,<break time="1s"/> to feel,<break time="1s"/> and to allow.<break time="4s"/>
</prosody>

